    • Method Detail

      • createDefaultService

        public static ChromeDriverService createDefaultService()
        Configures and returns a new ChromeDriverService using the default configuration. In this configuration, the service will use the chromedriver executable identified by the CHROME_DRIVER_EXE_PROPERTY system property. Each service created by this method will be configured to use a free port on the current system.
        Returns:
        A new ChromeDriverService using the default configuration.

      • createServiceWithConfig

        public static ChromeDriverService createServiceWithConfig​(ChromeOptions options)
        Configures and returns a new ChromeDriverService using the supplied configuration. In this configuration, the service will use the chromedriver executable identified by the CHROME_DRIVER_EXE_PROPERTY system property. Each service created by this method will be configured to use a free port on the current system.
        Returns:
        A new ChromeDriverService using the supplied configuration from ChromeOptions.
